{"id": "1210922982013407312", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 0, "author_id": "1201171926920482887", "author_name": "gerva1s", "author_bot": false, "content": "雖然想讓歡宴，多給一張防禦。但是想想還是太強了", "timestamp": "2024-02-24T12:15:36.773000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1210923042113327135", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 0, "author_id": "1201171926920482887", "author_name": "gerva1s", "author_bot": false, "content": "畢竟不存在➕傷痛已經三張了", "timestamp": "2024-02-24T12:15:51.102000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1210924052282212463", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 19, "author_id": "1201171926920482887", "author_name": "gerva1s", "author_bot": false, "content": "如果歡宴的加強考慮的是加強盾量，或許每回合第一次防禦50%+50%常規30%+30%是一個不錯的選擇", "timestamp": "2024-02-24T12:19:51.945000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1210895463012900894", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1210925821565608027", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 0, "author_id": "1200796523932438559", "author_name": "onest190", "author_bot": false, "content": "欢宴多点吧，和其他加强想比，一整局就加10黑印有点杯水车薪了。要知道盾量本就不富裕，这点黑印甚至没法多买一个刻印。", "timestamp": "2024-02-24T12:26:53.775000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1210926151892209674", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "不考慮啦，這兩個密契確實有一定定位重合，繼續競爭不是好事，也難以提高適用範圍並且可能對於極端情況太強，可能導致複製等等。我們本也有這個疑慮，所以緊急討論了一下修改z", "timestamp": "2024-02-24T12:28:12.531000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1201171926920482887"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1210924052282212463", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1210926182913155143", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 0, "author_id": "1201171926920482887", "author_name": "gerva1s", "author_bot": false, "content": "歡宴主要的問題是防御卡不夠，需要考不存在和傷痛一類來填補", "timestamp": "2024-02-24T12:28:19.927000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1210926774322466887", "channel_id": "1210881478653906985", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "前瞻的部分很可能因為測試幾個局面或者新考慮到某些組合而改動，因此相較正式修改會非常不穩定隨時修改。如果非常介意請忽略校貓日誌的前瞻內容。", "timestamp": "2024-02-24T12:30:40.930000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["426913095701495811"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1210917537693438012", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1210881478653906985", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅前瞻：「鑰令」與「密契」的增強", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
